      "Built and maintained event analytics layer — unpacking raw PostgreSQL event data, designing tracking logic, and syncing to Snowflake for downstream reporting",
      "Architected Snowflake ↔ Supabase integration for internal BI tooling migration; set up automated sync via GitHub Actions and managed full database schema in Supabase",
      "Designed and implemented multi-layer data models in Snowflake using dbt (bronze / silver / gold architecture), building the analytical foundation for internal BI dashboards and reporting",
      "Developed SQL transformation layers following Kimball dimensional modeling principles — fact and dimension tables powering Sales, Product, Marketing and Customer Success reporting",
      "Integrated and modeled data from multiple sources including CRM (Pipedrive), product analytics and internal operational datasets",
    ],
